{"h0860d7b7g1567g430eg8d97g756d7ab89547": ["*Whine.*", "63471e30-7413-4496-97de-0bdf67c2f753", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "59b44108-0ea1-b861-ee0e-713dda22c732"], "h5da7e03bg87a9g4c77g97a4gb598b66be3de": ["*Growl.*", "63471e30-7413-4496-97de-0bdf67c2f753", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "9898ed0d-bb12-8c12-24c4-56f57e13b75f"], "h9338bde5g489eg43c6gadf7g56a4c4eb7f3e": ["*Growl.*", "63471e30-7413-4496-97de-0bdf67c2f753", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "c5f9347f-3ca5-3c29-3ce8-29334d443256"], "h5e36a617g4963g4d1eg926ag421c647b5b29": ["<i>Try to get closer.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "a52c8c9c-e81d-95c5-e3ab-83a87d1d81e4"], "h4deaba00g3093g4111g9a0bgea50464aac68": ["*The wolf's fur bristles. He wants to jump, wants to <i>bite</i>.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "0504d8da-e46f-8e4e-c205-36c2ca51c28b"], "hc2f435c3g4171g41degaedfg0d3e6f22a35f": ["*His eyes dart back and forth as he sniffs the air. He can't see them anymore, but he can smell them. Many, many strangers.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "88130b66-f5fb-20e1-fceb-d7369c3ef345"], "h7b6a5b40g8339g45f2g92abg2640d2af0860": ["Go boy. Chase!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "16ad9c59-17fb-8cc8-ef87-e8982ac77ca8"], "h32f8f833gd5e9g4352gbf8dg77ac7b61c96b": ["*The wolf bares his teeth; he doesn't take orders from you. He would chase you down, if not for his master.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "5035c30e-ec07-e1d5-9d21-b6040a01f8fe"], "hbf9100efgdb76g4982g892dge51ca253bff0": ["Shh. It's all right.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "025dc336-42bc-f652-ddeb-414ed3df12ec"], "hee88d673ga29fg456fgba75g258669a90acd": ["<i>Sit next to him, murmuring softly while avoiding eye contact.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "2c8fcea0-d517-ed09-9fef-3e8a9b8e3138"], "hb3102645g0eefg4939gb443g3960120888e8": ["*His ears twitch as he lowers his head down into your lap.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "8f708270-ddca-2dac-7787-3bffb99b80ed"], "haf18bd4bg1f76g40c5gb453g181a32b8d3d8": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "88aa3954-b39d-02d6-a0d7-5fc61f7d8843"], "h0bb54872g2393g44bfg8235g15e524f99e1f": ["*A low growl builds in his throat as his eyes track the movement of your tail. It's agitating him.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "43785576-64e4-8730-acd1-4a997a7073cf"], "h4504394cg3db6g46aegb720g5d8eb25c2f91": ["Shh, I won't hurt you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "63924fc3-2a60-e54e-e901-89dd99bb6da6"], "h93e2b0b4g43c4g425bga14fg17a97d514f42": ["*His ears twitch as you speak, but his eyes don't shift from your tail. He sees you as a threat.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "770a7ec7-6d28-5344-f30a-4de72feda0f1"], "hbb2b5922gbde7g4215g88fbg471010f6b402": ["Down, boy.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "eed3d41b-817b-5d1e-bfaf-6e9dd6f4f96f"], "hd88e70e6g3377g40e5gaa3egc9f2ab74722b": ["*He snarls a warning, flattening his ears and lowering his body, ready to pounce.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "3c16f9c5-c2cb-c012-82aa-4dadcf09dcc6"], "hb2831d5bg1977g4a7aga647geb9912a4611b": ["*Snarl!*", "63471e30-7413-4496-97de-0bdf67c2f753", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "202cc06c-b294-1339-7fe0-ddd101f7cc09"], "h2d942fd0g8179g4548g8addg1581485aa890": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "c2984450-c351-533e-310a-3c097595546a"], "h0a6c6e7fg8319g488eg88ccgb7be7de8980f": ["*The wolf focuses on you, calmed in your presence.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "c6138f7e-3f9a-4221-a820-b3ca4e92dbfa"], "hc9b6cd48g1d0fg41eag9f20g5b86d174848e": ["Leave. You are not wanted here.", "63471e30-7413-4496-97de-0bdf67c2f753", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "815b067c-5ed9-6b43-9efd-e932817600ca"], "h8e1eaa63g6931g4262gb250gc74f2c0bb931": ["Another stranger come to vex me. What will you do? Hunt me? Grab my tail? Shout until my head hurts?", "63471e30-7413-4496-97de-0bdf67c2f753", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "efbcefda-20e1-6297-1e9a-0e5b10f889c5"], "he94b0cf5g11e8g4bafg8b03g8a6bd2b6612f": ["Relax. No one is here to hurt you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "0603e2a3-9627-897a-053e-b3f51aa38724"], "h10c275dcg5ccdg4074g8ab0g8afe403476c6": ["Stupid or a liar. Neither is needed here. <i>Go!</i>", "63471e30-7413-4496-97de-0bdf67c2f753", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "b71ed399-d70d-4c02-b5a1-8dd0338f1606"], "he523f012gd803g463dgadc5g64af1de22df7": ["Who's been pestering you? I'll teach them a lesson.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "ce96cc5d-35f6-9d00-051f-d6cc168af8fb"], "hf425a5c3gf643g4064gbedeg46600c891f13": ["Silence. <i>Your </i>help is not required. Not by <i>me, </i>at least.", "63471e30-7413-4496-97de-0bdf67c2f753", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "d1c39e21-62a2-5098-97bd-2288897a930e"], "hfe0a0c2bg1982g44c9ga811g233827bed812": ["I just wanted to give you my smell. I'll leave you be.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "b0aa9bc6-9399-70ee-af8e-f0c5d663d237"], "h0eb55ef1g9b88g4f16ga15ag0656da1193df": ["No - wait. You smell fresh. Safe. You can stay. If you must.", "63471e30-7413-4496-97de-0bdf67c2f753", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "ffb8cfed-1924-06c1-9e68-55fba609b209"], "h9d7240a9g7fcdg4640gb48ag2e9eb4274626": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_DruidPet_002.html", "4e769719-5de1-f2ca-5a5c-ad67ee724c2f"]}